          <img class="kharif" src="/public/images/kharif.jpg">
          <h3>Kharif</h3>
          <p>The Kharif season varies by crop and region.
            Rice is the most important Kharif crop of 
            India. Maize, jowar, bajra, tur, moong, urad, 
            cotton, jute, groundnut, soybean etc. are the
            other famous "kharif" crops.</p>
      </div>
